Class AbstractLogItem<T>

java.lang.Object
com.techhounds.houndutil.houndlog.loggers.Logger
com.techhounds.houndutil.houndlog.logitems.AbstractLogItem<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Loggable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BooleanArrayLogItem, BooleanLogItem, DoubleArrayLogItem, DoubleLogItem, FloatArrayLogItem, FloatLogItem, IntegerArrayLogItem, IntegerLogItem, StringArrayLogItem, StringLogItem, StructArrayLogItem, StructLogItem, TunableBoolean, TunableDouble
public abstract class AbstractLogItem<T> extends Logger
The base class for NT logging of primitive types. Can be used individually or grouped together in a LogGroup or DeviceLogger.
